      <h4>PowderKeg Labs (PKL)</h4>

      <p>PKL is a JavaScript software engineering consultancy specializing in rapid, iterative, feedback-driven, and data-driven development. We believe in the Lean methodology of "<i><b>launch fast, iterate faster</b></i>". Our goal is to deploy a version of your product, with only key features, as quickly as possible (the Minimum Viable Product). Then rapidly delivering new features on a continuous release cycle depending on user data and feedback.</p>

